  <script>
   window.SETUPS = window.SETUPS || (
		function () {
			var __ = {},
				exports = {__: __};
			__.stored = {};

			exports.set = function (key, value) {
				__.stored[key] = value;
			};

			exports.unset = function (key) {
				if (key in __.stored) {
					delete __.stored[key];
					return true;
				}
				else {
					return false;
				}
			};

			exports.get = function (key) {
				return typeof __.stored[key] !== 'undefined' ? __.stored[key] : null;
			};

			return exports;
		}());
  </script>
  <script>
   window.audi = window.audi || {};
	window.audi.api = window.audi.api || {};
	window.audi.api.lastConfiguration = window.audi.api.lastConfiguration || function () {
		var _storage = window.localStorage;

		if (!!_storage && _storage.lastConfiguration) {
			try {
				return JSON.parse(_storage.lastConfiguration);
			}
			catch (err) {
				console.warn(err);
				return false;
			}
		}
		else {
			return false;
		}
	};
  </script>

          <p class="sc-fzoWqW eesNcp">
           <span class="sc-jGYoDX kxMOQx">
            Stromverbrauch kombiniert
            <a class="audi-j-footnote-reference" data-reference-id="nemo-fn_eec-global-disclaimer" href="#nemo-fn_eec-global-disclaimer">
             <sup class="audi-footnote-anchor__text">
              *
             </sup>
            </a>
            :  20,2–19,3 kWh/100 km (NEFZ); 22,5–20,6 kWh/100 km (WLTP)
           </span>
          </p>
         </div>
         <div class="sc-kJeovx bpQcOD">
          <p class="sc-fzoWqW eLmVCQ">
           <span class="sc-jGYoDX kxMOQx">
            CO₂-Emission kombiniert
            <a class="audi-j-footnote-reference" data-reference-id="nemo-fn_eec-global-disclaimer" href="#nemo-fn_eec-global-disclaimer">
             <sup class="audi-footnote-anchor__text">
              *
             </sup>
            </a>
            : 0 g/km
           </span>
          </p>
         </div>
         <p class="sc-fzoWqW eLmVCQ">
          <span class="sc-jGYoDX kxMOQx">
           Angaben zu den Stromverbräuchen und CO₂-Emissionen bei Spannbreiten in Abhängigkeit von der gewählten Ausstattung des Fahrzeugs.
          </span>
         </p>
        </div>
       </div>
      </div>
     </div>
    </div>
   </feature-app>

         <li class="nm-model-band-container-item nm-model-band-container-types-item0" data-height="" data-index="0">
          <div class="nm-model-band-container-item-inner">

         <li class="nm-model-band-container-item nm-model-band-container-types-item1" data-height="" data-index="1">
          <div class="nm-model-band-container-item-inner">
           <div class="nm-model-band-container-headline">
            <label class="nm-model-band-container-close-button" for="nm-model-band-8276141-types-default">
             <svg class="audi-cancel-large-filled">
              <use xlink:href="/bin/nemo.static.20210322055156/cms4i-nemo/includes/core-ci/assets/icons/svg/system-cancel-large_black_filled.svg#audi-cancel-large-filled">
              </use>
             </svg>
            </label>

         <li class="nm-model-band-container-item nm-model-band-container-types-item9" data-height="" data-index="9">
          <div class="nm-model-band-container-item-inner">
           <div class="nm-model-band-container-headline">

          <div class="nm-model-band-container-item-inner">
           <div class="nm-model-band-container-headline">
            <label class="nm-model-band-container-close-button" for="nm-model-band-8276141-types-default">
             <svg class="audi-cancel-large-filled">

             </svg>
            </label>
            <span class="audi-headline-order-3 nm-model-band-container-headline-text">
             Roadster
            </span>
           </div>
           <ul class="nm-model-band-container-item-list">
            <li>
             <div class="nm-model-band-container-item-car-info">
              <a href="/de/brand/de/neuwagen/tt/tt-roadster.html">
               <picture>
                <source data-srcset="https://mediaservice.audi.com/media/live/50900/fly1400x601n8/fvr08y/2021.png?wid=291&amp;mimetype=image/webp" type="image/webp"/>

               </picture>
               <span class="nm-model-band-container-item-label audi-link-m">
                TT Roadster
               </span>
              </a>
             </div>
             <div class="nm-model-band-container-item-eec-info">
              <a href="/de/brand/de/neuwagen/tt/tt-roadster.html">
               <div class="nm-model-band-container-item-eec-info-label">
                <svg class="nm-icon-consumption">
                 <use xlink:href="/bin/nemo.static.20210322055156/cms4i-nemo/includes/core-ci/assets/icons/svg/consumption.svg#nm-icon-consumption">
